Mauritius’ Cargo Handling Corp. Seeking Partner, Quotidien Says

-- B y   K a m l e s h   B h u c k o r y
-- 
2011-04-07T11:03:31Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-07/mauritius-cargo-handling-corp-seeking-partner-quotidien-says.html
Cargo Handling Corp., Mauritius’s
state-owned port operator, is seeking a partner, Le Defi
Quotidien reported, citing company director Archimede Lecordier.  The decision to look for an investor is in line with a
recommendation from the  World Bank , the Port Louis-based
newspaper said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Kamlesh Bhuckory in Port Louis at 
 kbhuckory@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Antony Sguazzin at 
 asguazzin@bloomberg.net  